        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>There is a new passenger side upper panel to provide more head room above the passenger seat, for
                    9200, 9300 and 9400 Low Roof Pro Sleeper Models built from April 1, 1994 through May 1, 1995.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
